item.title: “It feels really good to be there”: Suryakumar Yadav acknowledges Number 1 T20I batter rank after winning Man of the Match in IND vs ZIM Super 12 match
item.description: “It feels really good to be there”: Suryakumar Yadav acknowledges Number 1 T20I batter rank after winning Man of the Match in IND vs ZIM Super 12 match The Super 12 stage of the tournament ended in a superb note for the Indian team where they registered a brilliant 71-run victory over Zimbabwe.
